lease-confirm.content:
Your booking confirmation details, dates and room(s) are shown below:
What happens next?


Familiarise yourself with our resident service portal where we communicate important information about this booking


We require the following additional documents to be uploaded to your resident service portal in pdf or jpg form (file size <1Mb) by no later than {0}:


Student ID
University admission letter

Once we receive the above documents from you our team will do this:


Check your application details and any requests
Verify your payment(s) are received
Send your Guarantor a lease agreement to e-sign, within 10 days
Counter sign the lease agreement
If we need more information from you we will email you, so look out for our emails
If we cannot accept your booking (for any reason) we will advise you within 10 days.

storey.msg.pre-application-checklist.Sig:
Reference #{{bookingNumber}}

Thank you for completing all the steps to secure your apartment — we can't wait for you to be settled in your new home.

Once your Residential Tenancy Agreement has been countersigned by Storey Residential, a copy will be available for download for your records.

If you need any assistance, feel free to reach out to us at +61 (0) 3938 40012 or living@storeyresidential.com.au
storey.msg.pre-application-checklist.App:
Welcome to Storey Residential!

Reference Number: #{{bookingNumber}}

Congratulations! Your lease application has been approved.

The next steps are to sign your lease and make your payments; you can complete these in any order.

Once both steps are completed, your apartment will be secured.

If you need any assistance, feel free to reach out to us at +61 (03) 3938 40012 or living@storeyresidential.com.au
storey.msg.application-complete-page.tha:
You're one step closer to your new home!

Thank you for completing the steps to secure your lease for {hotelName} - {roomTypeName} {roomNumber}.

Your Lease Reference is #{bookingNumber} - please keep this for future reference.

Next Steps:

Your lease will now be countersigned by our team. You will receive an email notification once it's available to download, for your records.

Storey will lodge your bond on your behalf with the Residential Tenancies Bond Authority (RBTA).

Keep an eye out for an email from the RTBA confirming your bond lodgement. Your bond receipt will be available within 10 days and will be sent to you via email.

We're looking forward to helping you settle in.
